# - try to find the Xrandr library
#
# Cache Variables: (probably not for direct use in your scripts)
#  XRANDR_INCLUDE_DIR
#  XRANDR_SOURCE_DIR
#  XRANDR_LIBRARY
#
# Non-cache variables you might use in your CMakeLists.txt:
#  XRANDR_FOUND
#  XRANDR_INCLUDE_DIRS
#  XRANDR_LIBRARIES
